  <Summary>The Goulish Revenge of Dr. Psycha: Dick Kirby, homicide cop assigned on occult cases, has to solve a friend's mysterious collapse into madness. He discovers a supernatural revenge plot.

Blood Vengeance!: In Paris, France, Henri Marbeau is possessed by the vengeful spirit of his ancestor who died on the guillotine. He has to kill the two last descandents of the rival DeVeau family.

The Witch's Wound: The sceptic Reginald spends a night at a haunted farm in Pennsylvania. Although not believing in witchcraft he is confronted with a horde of devilish cats.

Dr. Destiny: Dr. Destiny and his assistant Ramona investigate an eerie Transsylvanian castle which has been rebuilt on American soil. They exorcise the evil spirit of a "zhduh" incorporating the castle's owner.

